    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进入我们的冬季童话世界，在猫人国度里寻找正在玩耍的隐藏精灵、冬季甜点以及其他充满魅力的冬季元素。探索城镇边缘一个舒适的冬季森林，以及一座充满圣诞老人的工作坊的房子。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337920/extras/e9d970774428e392774b192d22fcc61b.poster.avif?t=1765227408\" width=800 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337920/extras/e9d970774428e392774b192d22fcc61b.webm?t=1765227408\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337920/extras/e9d970774428e392774b192d22fcc61b.mp4?t=1765227408\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>隐藏的冬季物品</strong>包括：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>隐藏精灵任务</strong>：在每个角落寻找顽皮的精灵和令人惊喜的冬季小物。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2个手绘冬季场景</strong>：体验两个充满美丽光芒的迷人场景。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>超过300个隐藏物品</strong>：寻找精灵、雪花、玩具、糖果、圣诞信封等等。你能找到所有的物品吗？</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>轻松的冬季音乐</strong>：完美沉浸于冬季氛围。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >循环场景。您可以随意旋转场景。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >非常希望能加入您的愿望单。这是我们的第一款游戏，对于我们的小团队来说非常重要。谢谢&lt;3</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337920/extras/ef0a6197d4ad2ad0bf46b61920957500.avif?t=1765227408\" width=800 height=198 /></span></p>",
